Tip - the Toronto Airport Express shuttle bus is a cost-effective mode of transport from the airport to the city.	This hotel has a slow parking garage elevator and forces you to call housekeeping if you want your bedding changed.	They arranged rental car service for us as well as airport transport.. All very reasonably priced and on time.	At checkout, we didn't have to pay for parking, as the same receptionist checked us out.	The hotel was very clean, the hotel staff were very friendly and information, and it was close to public transportation, which we used for our entire time in Toronto.	Parking is also expensive at $18 per day and the garage was small.